& more 🤍

node.text:
It’s AUSSIE time mate! This new collection is one we’ve been so excited to share with you!! We’re so grateful to have Copper Pearl in Australia and we wanted to show our support to all our Aussie friends with this new print! 

Check out the video above and let us know if you have any questions 👇🏼 we hope you ❤️ it as much as we do!

node.text:
“I just LOVE these swaddle blankets, they are the only ones I use! I just had my fifth baby so I’d like to think I have some experience in the blanket department, so trust me when I say these buttery-soft and ultra stretchy blankets make swaddling a breeze. Also, who can resist these adorable prints?? The pattern was vibrant and the perfect color for our newest addition to the family.” ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
📷 by @lauren_beckk

node.text:
🎥 @multitaskingmombrain

"It’s overwhelming some days, I see you ❤️ 

I’m working really hard on trying not to let the chaos that is life with three small children, overwhelm me, but it’s a challenge some days. 

Sometimes I need to step back and really remind myself that this WILL pass. And while I won’t miss the disasters all around me, I WILL miss my babies being this small. 

Also, there is something about these ordinary days. We put so much pressure on ourselves to give our kids all the best, most exciting, experiences, but sometimes the most fun is found in the simple things we do, just being together. 

So let my reminder today, be yours too. Try not to dwell so much on the daunting things that fill parenthood (I know it’s hard), instead let’s focus our sights on what’s really important, these little people, who are so rapidly growing before our eyes, and the ordinary days, as they are fleeting ❤️”
